{"tid":2311990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"盧俊宇被指浪費警力案 警再拘捕27歲男助理涉同罪","createTime":"2020-12-04T13:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T23:06:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c02f21827a75380fa843c615c8c29ffb9b5866df","tid":2311990,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:13:59.000Z","msg":"民主黨屯門區議員盧俊宇，7.21十五個月當日發帖聲稱自己在元朗被捕，其後刪帖，並澄清是與助理溝通有誤所致，但上周三（11月25日）仍遭警方以涉嫌浪費警力拘捕。事隔超過一星期，至今日警方稱經進一步調查後，今午約兩時在元朗區拘捕27歲姓趙男子，目前他仍被扣留調查。據知他為盧俊宇的助理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201204/U6D5SCJFXRAYJHIFKI3BCNVPLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201204%2FU6D5SCJFXRAYJHIFKI3BCNVPLI%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=f7fe1d5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201204%2FU6D5SCJFXRAYJHIFKI3BCNVPLI%2F&h=4bf08d28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201204/U6D5SCJFXRAYJHIFKI3BCNVPLI/</a>"},{"pid":"d3cb94e22aaac1b1751a8307074aea7ca7543ed4","tid":2311990,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf3fb39d00cb695ea1c521833fae7c14ac5d74b","tid":2311990,"uid":73972,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"咁都可以告浪費警力，不過好心就咪老作，完全多餘"},{"pid":"dd0fa282911e89e67e5bdd41a34dafc63c516136","tid":2311990,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:49:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46845be4fe4085178a84e3d508f19b982d11ba40","tid":2311990,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:05:05.000Z","m